  "summary": "This chunk details the ritual procedures for the Second and Third Days of a magical operation, including the use of pearls on charcoal, the drawing of two circles, and the invocation of specific planetary angels. It provides lists of angelic names categorized by their celestial spheres (Saturn, Jupiter, Mars, Sun, Venus, Mercury, Moon) and includes specific binding formulas using divine names.",
  "key_passages": [
    "place pearls on glowing charcoal in the censer, which [will be suffumigated] from the place (or direction) of invocation",
    "draw two circles, with one separated from the other by one foot, doing this with a new knife",
    "The third day, being bathed and putting on garments of clean white hemp, and the hairs from your body clean shaved",
    "O you mighty angels of Saturn, Jupiter, Mars, the Sun, Venus, Mercury, and the Moon",
    "I seal, beseech, invoke, and also conjure you to obey my petitions, through the seal of the sacred names of God"
  ]
